<node id="MODS">
  <data key="d0">MODS</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">MODS stands for Multiple Organ Dysfunction Score, a scoring system for organ failure.&lt;SEP&gt;MODS (Multiple Organ Dysfunction Score) is a scoring system used to assess organ dysfunction in the study.&lt;SEP&gt;MODS stands for Multiple Organ Dysfunction Score, a scoring system used to evaluate organ dysfunction.</data>
