<node id="SOFA">
  <data key="d0">SOFA</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">SOFA stands for Sepsis-related Organ Failure Assessment, a scoring system for organ dysfunction.&lt;SEP&gt;SOFA (Sequential Organ Failure Assessment) is a scoring system used to assess organ failure in the&lt;SEP&gt;SOFA stands for Sepsis-related Organ Failure Assessment, a scoring system used to evaluate organ failure.</data>
