  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The World Athletics Federation is the governing body overseeing the World Athletics Championship and record validations.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation is the governing body overseeing the World Athletics Championship and record validations.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation is the governing body overseeing the World Athletics Championship and record validations.</data>
