<node id="Impella">
  <data key="d0">Impella</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Impella is a catheter-based miniaturized rotary blood pump, specifically the Impella LP2.5 model, used for hemodynamic support in patients with cardiogenic shock.&lt;SEP&gt;Impella is a ventricular assist device used in patients with cardiogenic shock, associated with higher hemolysis and blood product administration compared to IABP.&lt;SEP&gt;Impella is a catheter-based, miniaturized rotary blood pump used as a new LVAD for percutaneous access in cardiogenic shock patients.&lt;SEP&gt;Impella is a medical device used as a treatment in a clinical trial, compared against intra-aortic balloon pump.&lt;SEP&gt;Impella is a medical device used for cardiac support, compared against IABP in a survival probability study.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-cd12a4d42988a0cbef608f813b7db575&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ff0702c16a40074abed0254fa2987a4d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a62a3411d190c14c03fad25d62150ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c33f31a24de4f3032f5ab5311fd13365&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c61ba2f73cda3eb90b84f74f9851e60</data>
  <data key="d4">seyfarth2008.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1780045976</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cardiogenic Shock">
  <data key="d0">Cardiogenic Shock</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Cardiogenic shock is a medical condition characterized by the heart's inability to pump sufficient blood, often caused by acute myocardial infarction.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-cd12a4d42988a0cbef608f813b7db575</data>
  <data key="d4">seyfarth2008.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1780045976</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Serum Lactate">
  <data key="d0">Serum Lactate</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Serum lactate is a metabolic parameter measured in patients, with lower levels observed in the Impella group during the first 48 hours.&lt;SEP&gt;Serum lactate is a biomarker of tissue perfusion and shock, measured over time in Impella and IABP patients.&lt;SEP&gt;Serum lactate is a biomarker measured to assess tissue hypoxia and metabolic status in patients.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-cd12a4d42988a0cbef608f813b7db575&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a62a3411d190c14c03fad25d62150ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c61ba2f73cda3eb90b84f74f9851e60</data>
  <data key="d4">seyfarth2008.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1780045976</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
