  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">A randomized clinical trial is the study&lt;SEP&gt;A Randomized Clinical Trial is the study design comparing Impella and Intra-Aortic Balloon Pump treatments.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-cd12a4d42988a0cbef608f813b7db575&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c33f31a24de4f3032f5ab5311fd13365</data>
