<node id="Baseline">
  <data key="d0">Baseline</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Baseline is the initial time point at which MODS and SOFA scores were measured before treatment.&lt;SEP&gt;Baseline is the starting point (Day 0) in the survival analysis before treatment randomization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ff0702c16a40074abed0254fa2987a4d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c33f31a24de4f3032f5ab5311fd13365</data>
