  <data key="d0">Glomerular Filtration Rate (GFR)</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Glomerular Filtration Rate is a measure of kidney function, estimated using cystatin C and creatinine, but not directly measured in this study.</data>
