  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Cystatin C eGFR is an estimate of kidney function based on cystatin C levels, used in propionic acidemia patients.&lt;SEP&gt;Cystatin C eGFR is a measure of kidney function based on cystatin C levels, used to estimate GFR in PA patients.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-61463c7b12c07a431ba8cba59dce8f00&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8a835d63382015bc0073fd6f79ae0ba</data>
